# Windsurf Rules

This repository is a Laravel 10 / PHP 8.4 enterprise real-estate platform with multi-tenant modular architecture. Keep changes focused and preserve proprietary semantics.

## Key References
- `AGENTS.md` — repository-specific agent guidance and conventions
- `README.md` — setup, environment configuration, module description
- `.github/agents/` — specialized agents for code review, deployment, frontend, testing, database, modules, environment

## Essential Commands
```bash
composer install --no-interaction --prefer-dist --optimize-autoloader
npm install && npm run build
composer test
composer run-script analyse
php artisan migrate --seed
```

## Architecture
- `app/Console/` — 141 scheduled Artisan commands
- `app/Http/Controllers/` — 306 module controllers
- `app/Models/` — Eloquent models per domain
- `app/Services/` — Domain service classes (prefer over controller logic)
- `app/Jobs/`, `app/Events/`, `app/Listeners/` — async and event-driven behavior
- `routes/api.php` — 1,700+ REST endpoints
- `resources/views/` — Blade templates organized by domain (CRM, HRMS, leads, properties, etc.)
- `resources/js/` — Vue 5 and Alpine.js components

## Development Guidelines
- Prefer service classes in `app/Services/` for business logic
- Keep REST API changes aligned with `routes/api.php`
- Preserve `.env.example` and never hardcode configuration
- Use `storage/app/documents/` and `storage/app/reports/` for generated files
- Validate behavior with tests before committing
- Avoid introducing new package dependencies unless explicitly requested

## Do Not Modify
- `.github/workflows/deploy.yml` — deployment controls, unless explicitly asked
- `.env.example` — preserve configuration structure
- Proprietary integrations (Razorpay, WhatsApp, MahaRERA, GST APIs)

## Frontend Stack
- Blade templates for server-rendered views
- Vue 5 for complex components
- Alpine.js for lightweight interactivity
- Tailwind CSS 3.4 for styling
- Chart.js, FullCalendar, DataTables, Leaflet, Select2 for specialized UIs
- Build: `npm run dev` (hot reload), `npm run build` (production)

## Indian Compliance & Real-Estate Domain
- GST/GSTR-1/3B, IRN e-Invoice generation
- RERA/MahaRERA project registration and compliance
- Stamp duty calculations
- PF/ESIC/TDS payroll compliance
- Aadhaar eSign, CIBIL integration
- Multi-tenant isolation for white-label verticals (Clinic, School, Hotel, Retail)

